data.description: Amazing Townhome in the coveted Waterford Subdivison. Home features almost 3,200 sq. ft. of living space with a huge master suite and closet. There is new central A/C and 2 gas fireplaces and a new furnace and water heater. The backyard is fully fenced with a large covered deck and full sprinkler system throughout. There are 2 neighborhood parks across the street and convenient location to all city amenities.  NEW LOWER PRICE!
